Package: SFD
Title: Spatial First Differences
Version: 0.0.1
Description: This package computes the Spatial First Difference (SFD) estimator using the lm function on transformed data. SFD is a simple research design that addresses unobservable heterogeneity in cross-sectional data. Please see: Druckenmiller & Hsiang (2018). 
Author: Hannah Druckenmiller [aut, cre],
    Solomon Hsiang [aut]
Maintainer: Hannah Druckenmiller <hdruckenmiller@berkeley.edu>
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2),
    stats, 
    utils, 
    graphics, 
    methods
Imports: sp,
    rgeos,
    raster,
    dplyr,
    magrittr
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
